      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity model selected for Ti-6Al-4V based on published stress-strain data (ASTM E8). Penalty contact with augmented Lagrangian enforcement used at screw-rod interface. Sensitivity study on friction coefficient (0.1–0.3) showed <4% variation in yield force. Gradation 3 achieved."
