    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single test condition; this shortfall is offset by the high degree of standardization provided by ASTM F1717 and the strong quantitative agreement across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96 for all). Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for the non-cannulated pedicle screw COU.",
